## Open Questions

> [!IMPORTANT]  
> 1. Do you want to allow Sellers to create their own **Categories**, or are Categories strictly managed by the **Admin** to maintain a clean storefront? (Usually, in multi-vendor apps like Shopee/Lazada, Admins manage the master categories).
> 2. Will variants always have a `price` (e.g., a Red shirt costs 500, a Blue shirt costs 500), or will the base product have a price and variants just add an `extra_fee`?

